{"tid":708012,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"倫常慘劇 歷年弒父母事件簿","createTime":"2018-06-19T04:48:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-19T11:28:24.000Z","uid":82917,"like":8,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"6f7043644b19e42e51f4a85854e57c84948dab56","tid":708012,"uid":82917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T04:48:19.000Z","msg":"新屯門中心發生弒父殺母的倫常命案，情況令人心酸，其實過往本港也曾發生同類案件，其中以大角嘴肢解父母雙屍案，最為轟動。<br />\n<br />\n03/2013：大角嘴肢解父母案<br />\n31歲周凱亮於大角嘴唐樓單位殺害及肢解六旬父母，周凱亮被判囚終身監禁；同伴謝臻麒謀殺罪名不成立，因非法處理屍體罪判處一年監禁。( <a href=\"http://bit.ly/1MNHiVV\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F1MNHiVV&d=QUqEOzsMfh%2BFED0Ir7pZ1viMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=c1f0f8ab\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/1MNHiVV</a> )<br />\n<br />\n03/2013：八鄉橫台山殺父傷母案<br />\n中菲混血兒霍立賢(21歲)與友人陳明天(22歲)，在八鄉橫台山寓所打機時被母親斥責，兩人聯手殺父傷母。兩人謀殺及企圖謀殺兩罪罪成，同被判處終身監禁。( <a href=\"http://bit.ly/1VZL2nS\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F1VZL2nS&d=QUqEOzsMfh%2BFED0Ir7pZ1viMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=7f53face\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/1VZL2nS</a> )<br />\n<br />\n01/2012：黃大仙摺凳殺父<br />\n醉酒男子陳松輝與75歲老父爭執，在黃大仙下邨住所以摺凳打死父親，被控一項謀殺罪，被判囚終身。( <a href=\"http://bit.ly/1KiDG85\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F1KiDG85&d=QUqEOzsMfh%2BFED0Ir7pZ1viMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=3a3a0271\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/1KiDG85</a>)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n08/2010：精神病女斬母頭顱<br />\n38歲疑有精神病女子，在黃大仙竹園邨家中斬甩70歲母親頭顱，然後燒屋跳樓死亡。( <a href=\"http://bit.ly/1LYkBt4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F1LYkBt4&d=QUqEOzsMfh%2BFED0Ir7pZ1viMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=ebb1be9f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/1LYkBt4</a> )<br />\n<br />\n07/2010：荃灣青年殺母軾妹<br />\n15歲失常少年在荃灣家中斬死12歲妹妹再殺死母親，報警自首，其後他被判入小欖治療中心接受無限期醫院令。( <a href=\"http://bit.ly/1MNHYe0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F1MNHYe0&d=QUqEOzsMfh%2BFED0Ir7pZ1viMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=aaeb2b77\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/1MNHYe0</a> )<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唉，睇到好心up。。。"},{"pid":"d4b5ba4b7bb2e11d42d6867790289b0a818d317f","tid":708012,"uid":82917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T04:48:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180618/58334747\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180618%2F58334747&d=QUqEOzsMfh%2BFED0Ir7pZ1viMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=8aa39d35\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180618%2F58334747&h=3e8ffb45\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180618/58334747</a>"},{"pid":"2ee478ddbca5f6aba48e1846f56779ad6851d6ad","tid":708012,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T04:58:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cec10620c96d510ca54128afea6deb3c3c052ec2","tid":708012,"uid":58140,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T05:01:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"638221ebcc9c1214f270fa3ffa2758f32ddd2d2e","tid":708012,"uid":4934,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T05:02:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d69023a4daa3dd003ef596b2dad1408edcc32bc","tid":708012,"uid":85193,"like":0,"dislike":24,"score":-24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T05:03:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8680301d6ec4f69b9989c31b239d44af2c9ce799","tid":708012,"uid":82917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T10:09:01.000Z","msg":"啲comment"},{"pid":"b21392a7df62185d29b78c1c070e10b8f2a26ab1","tid":708012,"uid":82917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8680301d6ec4f69b9989c31b239d44af2c9c